# Frontend / admin

- Follow existing page structure under `frontend/src/pages/admin/` and `adminApi.ts`.
- Admin actions: loading, disabled while in-flight, error message, success refresh — no silent failures.
- Preserve filters, city/destination selection, and pagination unless the task says otherwise.
- No broad visual redesign unless requested; Russian labels for admin-facing copy.

## API

Use `adminGet` / `adminPost` from `adminApi.ts`; handle 401/403 via existing session flow. Match backend response shapes; do not invent fields.

## Tests

Vitest + Testing Library for user-visible behavior: `frontend/src/**/*.test.tsx`.  
Run: `cd frontend && npm test -- --run` (narrow file when possible).

## Mobile

Keep admin tables/forms usable on small screens where practical; match existing `AdminDataPipeline.css` patterns.
